00:00:01,431 --> 00:00:24,254
Aham mawero homi, abhya bhaja homi, Anigo homi, sukhya tanang pariharami, Dukham ujjami, yathalada sampatito, Mavikacchami.

2
00:00:24,274 --> 00:00:30,239
Amakam chatupachaya dayaka,

3
00:00:30,591 --> 00:00:52,262
Awera hontu, abhya bhaja hontu, Aniga hontu, sukhya tanang parihalantu, Dukhamu chantu, yathalada sampadzito, Mawika chantu.

4
00:00:53,119 --> 00:01:21,472
A-ma-ka-ma-ta-pi-tu A-cha-ri-a-ny-a-ti-mi-ta-sa-mu-ha A-ve-ra-hon-tu A-pya-pa-ja-hon-tu A-ni-ga-hon-tu Su-ki-a-ta-na-ng-pa-ri-ha-lan-tu Du-ka-mu-chan-tu Ya-ta-la-da-sam-pa-ti-to

5
00:01:21,807 --> 00:01:50,817
MAUI GACCHANTU HIMASMINGVI HARE SABBE BIKKU SABBA BIKKUNI SABBE ACCHARYA SABBE YOGINO AWERA HONTU ABHYABHAJA HONTU ANIGA HONTU SUKHYATANAM PARIHARANTU

6
00:01:51,355 --> 00:01:59,463
Dukhamu chantu, yathalada sampatito, mawega chantu.

7
00:02:00,704 --> 00:02:10,996
Imas mingame, janapade, yoropaya, lukas ming, save janata.

8
00:02:11,896 --> 00:02:16,502
Awera hontu, abhya bhaja hontu.

9
00:02:16,987 --> 00:02:46,218
Ani gahontu sukhiyatanam pariharantu Dukhamu chantu yatala dasampatito Mawe gachantu Puratimaya disaya pacimaya disaya Uttaraya disaya dakhinaya disaya

10
00:02:46,772 --> 00:03:06,638
PURATIMAYANU DISAYA PACIMAYANU DISAYA UTTARAYANU DISAYA DAKINAYANU DISAYA HETIMAYA DISAYA UPARIMAYA DISAYA

11
00:03:07,207 --> 00:03:20,463
Sabhe sata, sabhe pana, sabhe bhuta, sabhe bhukala, sabhe atavavahariya pana.

12
00:03:21,284 --> 00:03:29,875
Sabha itiyo, sabhe purisa, sabhe ariya, sabhe anariya.

13
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:59,187
Sabe Deva, Sabe Manusa, Sabe Vinipatiha, Avera Hontu, Abhya Bhaja Hontu, Aniga Hontu, Sukhiya Tanang Parihalantu, Dukhamu Chantu, Yathalada Sampatito, Mawega Chantu.

14
00:03:59,891 --> 00:04:03,944
Kamasaka.
